Body: Description: Hello We are using an MDM solution (Mosyle) for our MAC workstations to set system permissions for applications. Is there a support document available that lists all of the permission and settings that need to be set when using Endpoint Protector on macOS devices? I found this document (https://www.endpointprotector.com/support/pdf/manual/Endpoint_Protector_5_JAMF_Deployment_User_Manual_5209_EN.pdf) but note sure if this is still applicable with later versions of Endpoint Protector. I appreciate your help.
What We've Learned Updated: We have provided the link to our latest JAMF deployment guide.
Next Steps Updated: We are waiting for the customer's feedback
